      *                          * Test se da stampare                 *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-num-doc-dpz        =    01
                     go to stp-tes-doc-052.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * String                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           string    "."
                                delimited by   size
                     w-num-doc-dpz
                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-num-doc-str
                                  with pointer w-num-doc-pnt          .
       stp-tes-doc-052.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
