      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-rig-num-ele          .
       stp-cor-doc-pcr-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start su righe documento [ocr]                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NUMPRT    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      "NL"                 to   f-cfr                  .
           move      w-rig-num-prt        to   rf-ocr-num-prt         .
