      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to stp-cor-doc-pcr-900.
       stp-cor-doc-pcr-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale file [ocr]                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/orc/fls/ioc/obj/iofocr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
